content:
The External Client App framework now supports all variations of the headless Authorization Code and Credentials Flow. Use this improved framework to set up headless login, passwordless login, and guest user identity flows in an off-platform app.

Where: These changes apply to LWR, Aura, and Visualforce sites accessed through Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
title: Summer '24 Release Notes
